Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:10.48,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking Hana back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:47.58,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi Manatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:51.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,do you realize what you're about to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:57.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping within this ship are \Nthousands of young men...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:00.39,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Young men entrusted with humanity's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:06.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to destroy their \Nlives and humanity's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:07.69,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:13.07,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is trying to save their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.07,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,What is the "life" you speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.41,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The boys sleeping within this ship
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:25.65,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,will face a future where only they \Nsurvive, locked in this iron box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.42,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,They'll sleep for thousands,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:34.71,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,tens of thousands of years, \Nperhaps forever, inside a spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.34,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:44.01,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The way I felt in that cold spaceship, \Njust watching time pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:46.50,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone else to experience that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.28,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:55.98,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they all want to run around, \Nfull of life, on that blue planet below!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:59.64,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the captain will make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot imagine that kid is prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Put down your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:12.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Pull that trigger, and you'll blow \Nup the whole {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This is a detonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:20.67,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If my vital signs stop, it will activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:25.76,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that I hold hostage \Nall the lives aboard the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:30.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine a member of the \NArk Faction like you would destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,all the young men sleeping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:38.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,With humanity's future at stake, you really \Nthink we wouldn't have a spare on hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:44.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We're prepared to make some sacrifices \Nto save humanity from extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:53.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've run a trace simulation on the enemy's actions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.75,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,to predict where the bombs are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:00.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But given that he's been moving about freely,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,we should assume he has inside help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There are other bombs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Give the bomb disposal team \Nthe estimated locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:09.81,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.22,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.15,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,"Midsummer's Knights"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:19.86,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Those lacking resolve cannot save this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.58,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi Manatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.15,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Especially not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:25.95,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:41.67,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We've no intention of unnecessarily \Nhurting those aboard the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:46.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Our primary objective is securing Hana Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.13,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And if Pointer screws up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:54.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, he'll be able rid us of our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:59.05,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop Operation Summer, whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:05.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the {\i1}Blume{\i0} belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.66,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,The Meaning of a Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:28.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but today's concert isn't an abreaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.25,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Blume{\i0} is in orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:38.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If they attack us, it'll pose a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:42.37,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If they convert their Orgone energy \Ninto pure physical energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:45.95,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,destroying an Ego Block is theoretically possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:48.30,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good chance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:53.04,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,they'll use the {\i1}Blume{\i0}'s Entangle Link to \Ndestroy the cocoon inside {\i1}Oberon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.55,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,That would be bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.71,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If we can, we should stop \Nthat disaster before it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.21,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ai, go up there and defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.18,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Why Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.49,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only one whose face they don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.37,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:11.17,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Using an idol who hides her face \Nwith sunglasses for a terrorist act?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.76,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Zin's singularity will be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Have him share it with you by telepathic kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.74,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:24.19,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,If the press sees that, there'll be total chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.38,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:31.82,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I think I like the way you try so hard in this video.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.78,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.57,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.21,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss scenes are also part of my job, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.19,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I found a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.24,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Pitz?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.60,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,This is Manatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:19.96,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hana's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It was Hirosue, from Salty Dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:28.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He has the detonator for the bombs \Nplaced on the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0} by Salty Dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:32.56,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Governor Yomatsuri, I'll send you \Nthe route we expect him to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:33.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forward it to security.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Security, you hear me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:41.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,From the estimated escape path,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:44.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,he likely escaped into the engine block.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:47.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The detonator is connected to his vital signs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so firearm use is prohibited!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he has kidnapped Hana Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.96,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,A meteoroid is approaching the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.87,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Spectral analysis has identified its constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:06.13,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Inconel... Probably the remnants of a spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.88,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see this debris in our catalog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't in our catalog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Bearing: 736.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Relative distance: 300,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Relative speed: 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We can't dodge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Collision in 750 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Estimated mass: 1,200 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Impact energy: 96 megajoules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough energy to penetrate \Nthe debris bumper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.60,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:34.43,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A large piece of debris is heading for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:35.79,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Debris?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Just get Hana back as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.16,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I won't know what Pitz is saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.91,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with Pitz?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:48.92,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Just before we found the debris, \NPitz started freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.44,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Because Hana was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:54.90,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is just my intuition as a magical girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,but something else is going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You follow Hirosue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.09,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.68,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Daichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:05.42,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.98,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Governor, Teppei is headed \Nfor the Nebula Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Have him launch as soon as he's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:12.72,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Target sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.43,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The target has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.05,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,A new meteoroid is incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Bearing: 927.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Relative distance: 350,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Relative speed: 420.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Impact in 833 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:54.07,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no record of this debris in the catalog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.11,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Estimated mass: 2,800 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:10:00.28,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we couldn't detect \Nthe orbit of debris this size...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.92,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Footage incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.88,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The target has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A second one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:21.51,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did my test attract too much attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of debris in orbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:35.19,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I have all kinds of toys ready \Nto give as gifts my fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Violent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:37.90,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:40.41,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ticket to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.41,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,More debris incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.34,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-five in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.41,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.37,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:48.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.41,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.76,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Relative distance: 320,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.60,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Relative speed: 420.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.68,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Impact in 780 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.06,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:17.03,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,But how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They dodged?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:27.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Nebula.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the debris is heading your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:33.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:39.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Propulsion, communication, and \Nejection systems are all down...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:41.97,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The Nebula Engine has been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.97,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The debris has passed the Nebula, \Nand is heading for the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.35,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,More debris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:50.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Teppei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.50,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The communication system is offline?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.42,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,This is Manatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Nebula has been damaged and \Nknocked out of commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.49,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.84,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The debris is on course for the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Head out in the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:07.87,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:11.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0} itself is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.41,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:17.77,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Even more debris has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.78,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What is Pitz saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Forty-seven... Forty-eight... Forty-nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:21.94,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It keeps coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:22.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:26.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,MM bus signal detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Epicenter identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.77,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.33,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the transport ship {\i1}Nipper{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:40.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Security Team 64, get to space port {\i1}Nipper{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:51.30,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Governor, there's even more debris coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the times for this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:10.03,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The main event's just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.85,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Over five hundred pieces of debris incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:17.48,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming in at relative speed: 620.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.44,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:32.33,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we'll use the boosted plasmagnum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:35.09,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But we haven't even tested it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:38.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way to survive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:39.79,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:43.93,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.14,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Boosted plasmagnum, stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.92,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Boosted plasmagnum, scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The Marine Gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.79,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Target confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:02.89,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Boosted plasmagnum, ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:10.51,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get the Nebula out \Nof there, or Teppei-kun will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Nebula can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Its propulsion system has been \Ndestroyed, and we can't contact it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.66,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The ejection system is probably damaged, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:27.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.89,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't fire now, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:31.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:37.55,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You go to the {\i1}Blume{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:42.30,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,and promise me you'll save humanity's chosen ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:44.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.63,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:53.26,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Only those with the necessary \Nresolve can save humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:03.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.08,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,An amazing amount of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:03.22,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Is this that boy's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.79,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It may be just as King said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:14.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We can entrust our hopes to that team.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:26.52,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,All objects in the firing radius \Nhave been annihilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:29.11,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's a signal where the Nebula was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.70,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:53.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Nebula Engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.15,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,DC?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:31.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What is that machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What is that Orgone energy light?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.93,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is Matsui, with Security Team 64.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.80,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We've found a suspicious object \Nin the {\i1}Nipper{\i0} cargo room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A Machine Goodfellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,And it's active!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.95,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy that capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.15,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:51.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it when my fans ambush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.37,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The event's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:13.75,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This is Security Team 64.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:16.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We destroyed the capsule, but the object fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:19.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We will continue searching for the bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Had our positions been reversed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I would have fired 2.5 seconds faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You still aren't strong enough, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get Hana back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:05.50,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:21:00.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,My mission is to kidnap Hana Mutou \Nand eliminate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:10.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know Teppei Arashi would survive that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:16.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you the kind of man who \Nwould let one of his friends die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:26.79,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going to kill \NTeppei with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:30.50,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't going to "let him die."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.59,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,If he'd died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.44,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been because I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:43.04,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't afford to hesitate there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:51.46,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:53.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:56.62,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:02.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really defeat the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:09.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really save Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:16.63,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If you really can...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:22.48,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:25.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:28.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Save the planet where everyone lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:31.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If you really can...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:38.90,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Please save them, Captain Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:18.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the time has come to destroy \Nthe enemy fortress carrier {\i1}Oberon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:21.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That very moment, Alonzo tells \Nus the Planetary Gears are
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:23.25,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,launching an all-out attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.25,0:24:25.04,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.04,0:24:29.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But Salty Dog's ultimate weapon stands before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.69,0:24:30.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting in our way?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.94,0:24:33.46,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This plan is for the Earth's protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 22 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.28,0:24:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Operation Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.28,0:24:38.37,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Operation Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.80,0:24:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, expand!
